com.intechcore.scomponents.scell.api.spreadsheet.model.style

Interface IStyle


  • public interface IStyle
    Represents the common style of a single cell or a range of cells. The value of the property is not null, when all cells from the selected area have the same value of the property. The value of the property is null when the style of a cell or cells is different from the styles of the other cells in the range
